snippet.title: The Texas Chain Saw Massacre - Unrated Gameplay Trailer [4K]
snippet.description:
The Unrated Cut of the brand new gameplay trailer for The Texas Chain Saw Massacre, a game based on true events, by Gun Interactive and Sumo Digital.

For more information, check out The Texas Chain Saw Massacre at TXChainSawGame.com and find us on the following social platforms:

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/TXChainSawGame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TXChainSawGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/TXChainSawGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TXChainSawGame

ESRB Rating Pending.
